<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Bernhard I., Herzog von Braunschweig-Lüneburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Herausgabe eines beschlagnahmten Fässleins mit Pelzwerk des Konrad Kreß, Bürger zu Nürnberg, zumal Nürnberg von den angeführten Achtbriefen des königlichen Hofgerichts nicht betroffen ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="106r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l19"><expan>B<ex>er</ex>nhart</expan> <expan>hertʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Prawnſſvv<ex>eig</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l20">vnd cʒu lünemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l21"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>vo<ex>r</ex>mals</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / von des veſʒleins <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l22">mit <expan>Schönemvve<ex>r</ex>gk</expan> / Als Jr dem C Kreſſen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> laſʒen habt / darauf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l23">vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / vnd <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geſchribe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / daʒ Jr Achtbrief von des 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>hell<ex>e</ex>r</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l24"><expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römiſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reichs <expan>hofger<ex>iht</ex></expan> habt etc Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Nu trifft dieſelb ſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l25"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr Achtbrief habt / vns / noch die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht an / vnd vvir vviſʒen anders </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l26">niht / dann daʒ vvir hoffen / vnd <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ vvir wol in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein / vnd ſo hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l27">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> das <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> veſʒlein mit <expan>ſchöne<ex>m</ex></expan> vvergk / voꝛ vns mit ſeinem eide behabt / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l28">als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> das voꝛ <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben / <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l29"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> / dem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das ſein noch <expan>gnedigl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſchick<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>laſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l30">Als etc / das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="106r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>B<ex>er</ex>nhart</expan>, <expan>herczog<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Prawnssw<ex>eig</ex></expan> und czu Lünemburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                                <expan>vo<ex>r</ex>mals</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> von des veszleins
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>schönem we<ex>r</ex>gk</expan>,
                        als ir dem <expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Kressen,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>aufgehalt<ex>en</ex></expan> laszen
                        habt; darauf uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, daz ir achtbrief von des
                                <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs <expan>hofger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
                        habt etc. Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, nu trifft dieselb sache,
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ir achtbrief habt, uns noch die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht an und wir wiszen anders niht,
                        dann daz wir hoffen und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir wol in
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, und so hat der
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> das <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
                        veszlein mit <expan>schöne<ex>m</ex></expan> wergk vor uns mit seinem eide
                        behabt, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> das vor
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochw<ex>irdikeit</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dem <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das sein
                        noch <expan>gnedigl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>schick<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>volge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasze<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
